'''Aɣyay''' d amur alemmas n [[abelkim|ubelkim]] anda i [[azenẓi|tezzenẓay]] deg-s tkura n ubelkim akken i d-ittnulfa degs wamur meqqren n takura-ines seg [[Apṛutun|yipṛutunen]] ilawen n [[taggat tazarurant]] d [[neutron|yinyutrunen]] yemgadan deg taggat,  i wakken ad yili weɣyay s unalkam d ilaw n taggat, ma d taggat n iprutunen tilawt deg umḍan tegda taggat n iliktṛunen ibawen, ayen yettaǧǧan abelkim ad yili yemgada deg tazrura. 

[[Akdu]] n weɣyay iga gar n 1,75 fm (1.75×10<sup>−15</sup> m) i [[Hidṛujin|uhidṛujin]] (ayen yegdan [[aqqaṛ]] n yiwen n upṛutun) alamma d 15 fm i yibelkimen imeqqranen n tkura am [[uranium]]. Iseggiwen-a meẓẓiy-it s waṭas ɣef wakdu n ubelkim (s wazal n 23 000 n tikkal i wuranium d 145 000 n tikkal i uhidṛujin). 

Afurk n tfizikt i d-yelhan s tezrawt d tigzi n weɣyay n ubelkim s wayen yellan deg tsuddest-ines yettusemma s [[Tafizikt tabelkamt|tfizikt tabelkamt]].

